snippet.title: Angra - Stand Away (Cover by SIEG ft. Daniel Bernal)
snippet.description:
Siegfried Song Facebook : http://www.facebook.com/SiegfriedSongOfficial
Daniel Bernal YouTube : https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCffwTOnMtcOnYjuKAmx3b3A

Angra - Stand Away (Cover by SIEG)

André Matos is one of the vocalists who influenced me the most. I used to just imitate his vocals at that time but since my vocalization has changed a lot from the days, so it’s been very challenging to relive the old style while adding some of my originality. In fact, I cried several times because I couldn't get my voice out but I made it and here is the result.

I am so grateful for Daniel's wonderful track. He also graciously gave permission to use this track. Please visit his channel. Thank you.

Siegfried Song (Symmetric Chaos, South Korea) - Lead Vocals, Video Editing, Mastering
Daniel Bernal (Daniel Bernal, Brazil) - Rhythm Guitars, Bass Guitars, Drum Programming, Mixing
